<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="invite-vt">invite <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'vaɪt/    美 /ɪn'vaɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>邀请：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why don't we <strong>invite</strong> our new neighbour over <strong>for</strong> tea?
我们为何不请新邻居过来喝茶呢？</p></div>

<ul>
<li>invite sb to (do) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>invite friends to the party
邀请朋友参加聚会</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We did so well that we were invited to share our idea and experience with all the students of our school.
我们做得很出色，应邀向全校学生分享我们的想法和经验。</p><footer>2016 北京书面表达</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>请求；征求</strong></h4>
<p>to ask sb formally to do sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A TV programme, Hero Show, is inviting students'  opinions on what qualities heroes and heroines should have.
电视节目《英雄秀》正就英雄应该具备什么样的品质征求学生的意见。</p><footer>北师大① – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>招致 (尤指坏事)</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>On the last day of our week-long stay,we<strong><em>_</em></strong>_(invite) to attend a private concert.  （2019全国）  </li>
<li>When summer comes, they will invite their students pick the fresh vegetables!  （2017 全国  改错）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. were invited  2. pick 前加to  </p></div>